text.section:
Within 90 days after executing a search, contact, and reunion services agreement under § 5-4B-05 or § 5-4B-11 of this subtitle, a confidential intermediary shall file a report with the Director stating that:
the individual contacted by the confidential intermediary consents to the disclosure of specified information;
the individual contacted by the confidential intermediary does not consent to the disclosure of any information;
the individual sought by the confidential intermediary has not been located; or
the individual sought by the confidential intermediary is deceased.
